            <h2 class="text-center">Annual Conference, Autumn 2025</h2>
            <h3 class="text-center"><i>An arresting day out in Inveraray: prison records and their use in historical research</i></h3>
            <figure>
                <img src="/assets/sra-conference-autumn-2025.png" alt="Eighteenth-century woodcut showing a woman in a prison cell"/>
